=== Infection Documentation Protocol

Participants document each illness with:
    - Date of symptom onset
    - Presumed pathogen (viral vs.\ bacterial, if identifiable)
    - Symptoms (upper respiratory, gastrointestinal, systemic)
    - Severity (1–10 scale)
    - Time from symptom onset to antiviral treatment initiation (if applicable)
    - Antiviral agents used and duration
    - PEM response (crash triggered yes/no, severity if yes, recovery duration)
    - Estimated baseline functional impact 2 weeks post-infection recovery


